Module org.eclipse.persistence.moxy
Package org.eclipse.persistence.jaxb.javamodel.xjc

Class XJCJavaFieldImpl

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.persistence.jaxb.javamodel.xjc.XJCJavaFieldImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
JavaField, JavaHasAnnotations
public class XJCJavaFieldImpl extends Object implements JavaField
INTERNAL:

Purpose: JavaField implementation wrapping XJC's JFieldVar. Used when bootstrapping a DynamicJAXBContext from an XML Schema.

Responsibilities:

  • Provide Field information from the underlying JFieldVar.
Since:
EclipseLink 2.1
